| Konachan                    | [Documentation](https://konachan.com/help/api)                         | :x:                |
| Waifus.im                   | [Documentation](https://waifu.im/)                                     | :x:                |
| Catboys                     | [Documentation](https://catboys.com/api)                               | :x:                |

